snippet.title: MetroNashville
snippet.description:
Informative television programming of the Metropolitan Government of Nashville & Davidson County Tennessee.  The MetroGovNashville YouTube Channel is administered by MNN (The Metro Nashville Network), a division of the Information Technology Services Department of Metro Government.  For more information, visit nashville.gov or nashville.gov/MNN

Visit us on facebook: https://www.facebook.com/MetroNashvilleNetwork/
